            <p>Cards that help users understand the sort of care they need.</p>   
        </div>

        <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-one-third">
            <h2 class="nhsuk-heading-s nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-3"><a href="/patterns/do-and-dont-lists">Do and Don’t lists</a></h2>
            <p>Help users understand what they should and shouldn’t do.</p>  
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nhsuk-grid-row nhsuk-u-margin-top-8">
        <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-one-third">
            <h2 class="nhsuk-heading-s nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-3"><a href="/patterns/footer">Footer</a></h2>
            <p>Helps users find links they expect at the bottom of our pages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-one-third">
            <h2 class="nhsuk-heading-s nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-3"><a href="/patterns/header">Header</a></h2>
